591
00:41:29,862 --> 00:41:32,614
Throwing bread in a hole didn't feed Africa.

592
00:41:32,781 --> 00:41:33,865
A kid's game!

593
00:41:34,200 --> 00:41:36,409
As for your treasure, keep it!

594
00:41:36,785 --> 00:41:39,746
