595
00:41:39,914 --> 00:41:42,290
- Thank you, Dr Freud.
- Here...

596
00:41:44,210 --> 00:41:46,169
Won't find that where you are.

597
00:41:46,545 --> 00:41:48,046
It's why I live there.

598
00:41:49,882 --> 00:41:52,008
